data.description: Charm & Character!!If you have been searching for a home on OVER AN ACRE in the heart of Navarre, then stop your search right here! This home has a new roof, has an added front gate entrance, and tons of new wood work added to the home. The home attracts tons of natural lighting and has such a warm inviting feeling upon the entrance. The long deep driveway leads to the double garage and more property to the right side where the pergola lounge area sits. Enjoy bringing your recreational toys home when you don't have an HOA here! Only 9-11 minute drive to Navarre Beach and a very close commute to Hurlburt Field AFB. This is a rate opportunity to own a large parcel with such a well maintained charming home. Come see all the details for yourself. PDF Survey, wind mit, & low insurance.
